	(text_box "Each LED draws ~20mA assuming a VF of 3.2V and a resistor of 92.5Ω.\nEach layer of LEDs can consequently draw a max of ~980mA.\nOnly one layer must be on at a time.\n\nThe voltage drop across the MOSFET and BJT (Vce) is 0.05V.\n"
